 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Luis Alvarez/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>On our previous coverage of Universal Health Realty Income Trust (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UHT\" title=\"Universal Health Realty Income Trust\">UHT</a></span>) we explained our rationale as to why we exited the stock at $41.76 and also went over why we chose for a long</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1166090290/image_1166090290.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742752-universal-health-realty-7-3-percent-yield-27-years-of-hikes", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 08:56:34"}, {"id": "4742751", "title": "FinWise Bancorp: Pricey For A Reason", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Mobile payment. Woman\"s hand has smartphone with banknote in the sky.' data-id=\"1049192158\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3714px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1049192158/image_1049192158.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/get