tic.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The Dividend Champions list is a monthly compilation of companies which have consistently increased their annual dividend payouts. However, since this list is only produced once per month, the data in it can quickly get out of date. Furthermore, with around 700</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742748-dividend-champion-contender-challenger-highlights-week-of-december-8", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 08:37:35"}, {"id": "4742759", "title": "ISM Services PMI Expanded For Fifth Straight Month In November", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"project management institute concept with symbols PMI on wooden blocks\" data-id=\"1499812958\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Maks_Lab</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Institute of Supply Management (ISM) has released its November services purchasing managers' index (PMI). The headline composite index is at 52.1, worse than the forecast of 55.5. The latest reading moves the index back into expansion territory for the 51st time in the past 54</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742759-ism-services-pmi-expanded-fifth-straight-month-november", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 08:35:00"}, {"id": "4742746", "title": "Phillips 66: Refiners Are 'Deer In The Headlights' Of Canadian Import Tariffs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458293517/image_458293517.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Phillips 66 gas station\" data-id=\"458293517\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3888px\" height=\"2592px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/gett